	- rounds[currentRoundNumber].ticketsSold == 0
	- rounds[currentRoundNumber].blockNumber == 0 || block.number - 256 > rounds[currentRoundNumber].blockNumber
	- block.number == rounds[currentRoundNumber].blockNumber
